    <item>
      <title>司法部最快周四起诉苹果违反反垄断法</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-20/doj-to-sue-apple-for-antitrust-violations-as-soon-as-thursday</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国司法部准备最早于周四起诉苹果公司，指控这家全球第二大市值科技公司阻止竞争对手访问其 iPhone 的硬件和软件功能，违反了反垄断法。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-20/doj-to-sue-apple-for-antitrust-violations-as-soon-as-thursday</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 20 Mar 2024 21:22:39 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>人工智能增长有助于增强收入预测，美光股价飙升</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-20/micron-soars-after-ai-opportunity-helps-bolster-revenue-forecast</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国最大的计算机存储芯片制造商美光科技公司(Micron Technology Inc.)在人工智能硬件需求的提振下，对本季度的收入做出了令人惊讶的强劲预测，随后股价在尾盘上涨。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-20/micron-soars-after-ai-opportunity-helps-bolster-revenue-forecast</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 20 Mar 2024 20:09:02 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>据《华尔街日报》报道，Apollo 斥资 110 亿美元收购派拉蒙工作室</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-20/apollo-offers-11-billion-for-paramount-studio-wsj-reports</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据《华尔街日报》援引知情人士消息称，阿波罗全球管理公司提出以 110 亿美元收购派拉蒙全球好莱坞工作室。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-20/apollo-offers-11-billion-for-paramount-studio-wsj-reports</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 20 Mar 2024 18:49:17 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>微软因在中国审查必应而招致越来越多的批评</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-20/microsoft-attracts-growing-criticism-for-censoring-bing-in-china</link>
      <description><![CDATA[第二位美国参议员攻击了微软公司在中国的业务，继《彭博商业周刊》对其在华审查必应搜索引擎的方式进行调查后，人权组织发起了一系列批评。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-20/microsoft-attracts-growing-criticism-for-censoring-bing-in-china</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 20 Mar 2024 18:12:50 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Meta、微软、X 联手反对苹果的应用商店计划</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-20/meta-microsoft-x-band-together-against-apple-s-app-store-plans</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Meta Platforms Inc.、微软公司、X Corp. 和 Match Group Inc. 请求联邦法官驳回苹果公司向外部支付选项开放其 App Store 的计划。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-20/meta-microsoft-x-band-together-against-apple-s-app-store-plans</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 20 Mar 2024 18:00:11 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Epic Games 今年将在 iOS、Android 平台上开设商店</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-20/epic-games-will-open-store-on-ios-android-platforms-this-year</link>
      <description><![CDATA[广受欢迎的《堡垒之夜》系列游戏的开发商 Epic Games Inc. 宣布了在 iOS 和 Android 平台上推出移动在线商店的计划。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-20/epic-games-will-open-store-on-ios-android-platforms-this-year</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 20 Mar 2024 17:55:38 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Astera 首次公开募股 7.13 亿美元后，人工智能推动需求飙升 72%</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-20/astera-soars-46-after-713-million-ipo-snapped-up-on-ai-demand</link>
      <description><![CDATA[半导体连接公司 Astera Labs Inc. 的首次公开募股（IPO）筹集了 7.13 亿美元，超出预期，在首次公开募股中股价上涨 72%，为人工智能相关股票和上市反弹增添了动力。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-20/astera-soars-46-after-713-million-ipo-snapped-up-on-ai-demand</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 20 Mar 2024 16:54:23 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>拜登关于汽车排放的最新规定将促进电动汽车销售</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-20/biden-set-to-boost-electric-car-sales-with-new-epa-rule</link>
      <description><![CDATA[拜登政府周三采取行动，遏制美国汽车和轻型卡车的污染，实行严格的尾气排放限制，这将迫使汽车制造商迅速提高电池电动和插电式混合动力车型的销量。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-20/biden-set-to-boost-electric-car-sales-with-new-epa-rule</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 20 Mar 2024 15:30:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>兴登堡在新报告中押注数据中心所有者 Equinix</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-20/hindenburg-bets-against-data-center-owner-equinix-in-new-report</link>
      <description><![CDATA[周三，卖空者兴登堡研究公司（Hindenburg Research）瞄准了数据中心所有者 Equinix Inc.，指控该公司操纵其会计并正在出售“人工智能白日梦”。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-20/hindenburg-bets-against-data-center-owner-equinix-in-new-report</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 20 Mar 2024 13:14:59 GMT</pubDate>
